				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3>Multi Langauge Typing select opiton</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>Hi,<br /><br />&nbsp; In my application, I would like to enable one option for admin to select the language for replying according to the user/client&nbsp; typed language. How to enable this option and change language typing.<br /><br /> My idea is to change this tag in JSP .<br /><br />&lt;SCRIPT language=JavaScript src=&quot;script/telugu.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;<br /><br />Here if we can change telugu.js to hindi.js or tamil.js Etc., on admin language selection we can achive this.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(or) <br />Complete replace of above tag with hindi or tamil tag.<br /><br />can we do this change using java script??? <br /><br />provide me the sample code.<br /><br />I hope u understand my problem.<br /> <br />can u explain me how do this for same session and single, same page reload&nbsp; with out previous session change.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Thanks&amp;Regards,<br />Vijay Kumar,<br />Software Engineer.</div>
			</div>
			<div class="clearer"></div>
